Steam Friends Status
--------------------

System Requirements:
Python is needed to run the basic command-line version: cli/steamfriends2.py
PyQT4 is required for the GUI version of Steam Friends Status: steamfriends

Running Steam Friends Status:
To run the GUI version, execute steamfriends in the root of the git repository.
To run the command-line version, execute steamfriends2.py under the cli/ folder.

Steam Identity:
Your steam identity is two things, both of which can be found in the steamcommunity.com URL.

Short Name: http://www.steamcommunity.com/id/$n
ID Number: http://www.steamcommunity.com/profiles/$n

